NS-CWP-005 — DECISION (Reissued)
Cognitive Work Plane (CWP)
Purpose
Defines operational decision-making in CWP (assignment, scheduling, supervision, escalation, closure) with explainability and human override.
Decision Classes
  Work Creation
  Assignment
  Scheduling
  Supervision
  Escalation
  Closure
Decision Artifact (Logical)
  decision_id, decision_type, work_ref
  inputs_summary, outcome
  ruleset_version, decided_at, actor_id
