NS-CWP-006 — VERSION (Reissued)
Cognitive Work Plane (CWP)
Purpose
Defines append-only versioning for work artifacts, agent capabilities, SLAs, and decision rulesets to ensure replayability and audit.
Versioned Artifacts
  Task/Mission/Program definitions
  Agent capability profiles
  SLA definitions
  Decision rulesets
  Escalation policies
